{"tid":980483,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[有酬］尋鸚鵡啟事（黃大仙區 獅子山）","createTime":"2019-01-13T14:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T13:59:55.000Z","uid":70939,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"871803e755f2eaf8713c81c8c83a2557d15ad802","tid":980483,"uid":70939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:12:37.000Z","msg":"我就黎出camp既時候啱啱收到通知<br />\n屋企隻鸚鵡仔Beedo走失左<br />\n希望連登有愛，幫手推一推等Beedo可以盡快番屋企<br />\n<br />\n姓名：Beedo<br />\n走失地方：獅子山公園<br />\n品種：葵花鸚鵡<br />\n特徵：個喙有痕<br />\n走失時間：2019年1月13日約下午5點<br />\n<br />\n臨入camp前我一路都係佢既剷屎官，剷左兩年幾，我唔開心時輕輕地抱住佢佢唔會走，佢好乖好鐘意人摸佢個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n寵物主人電話：96599809 （翁小姐）<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手推一推，等多d人喺附近都可以幫手望下，thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOiDHXr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOiDHXr.png&h=1790e0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inUSNo8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinUSNo8.png&h=eeb8bdd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9OPb2Xu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9OPb2Xu.png&h=c2a118c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYQq7pa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYQq7pa.png&h=a83f4a4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af77984ae66ddb47ac33fc3949333121e00490f5","tid":980483,"uid":38989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n希望可以搵番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d921697ee2d7ce8163da3109d5459be91242aa54","tid":980483,"uid":38989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":